{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回\"匆匆七年\"讲述了裴珏在飞龙镖局的成长经历。时过七年，蒙面客与中州一剑已被人淡忘，龙形八掌檀明的声望日隆。裴珏身为\"枪剑双绝\"裴扬之子，虽刻苦练武却进展甚微，连大洪拳都练不出根基，内心自卑忧郁。檀明只教他们粗浅功夫，不准观看镖师练武，裴珏虽有怀疑却不敢言。每日清晨他独自练拳，与年幼聪慧的袁泸珍相依为伴。檀明之女檀文琪娇憨任性，常以石子掷裴珏取笑其笨，二人在踢毽子的嬉戏中渐生情愫。裴珏暗中苦练毽子技艺，在比赛中大胜檀文琪，一时忘情亲吻了她。恰被檀明撞见，檀明面如寒冰厉声呵斥女儿回房。裴珏深受刺激，望着蚂蚁搬运食物顿悟自身处境，决心离开镖局外出闯荡。他翻越围墙，毅然踏上了独自闯荡江湖的路。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "怪不得我爹爹说你笨，你瞧你，练了这么久的功夫，有人在后面暗算你，你都不知道，这幸好是石头，要不，你脑袋不开花才怪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你拳练完了没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你呀！真气死人，人家跟你说话，你总是像哑吧似的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "我知道，我们不配跟你说话，只有你的袁妹妹才配跟你说话是不是？好！以后你不要理我好了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "text": "琪妹——",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "真讨厌，谁教你理我的？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "谁要和我踢毽子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你跟不跟我踢毽子？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "text": "踢！踢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "这才乖。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "喂，你怎么不帮我数呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "两百个踢完了，该轮到你啦！要是你踢不到两百个，看我今天可饶你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "text": "假如我踢到了呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "唷，敢情你还能踢两百个呀！好，你踢到两百个随便怎样都行。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "text": "随便怎样都行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你坏死了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "好，你真坏，偷偷地去学了是不是？也不告诉我，让我上当。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你坏，你坏！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "text": "你输了，还赖。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "檀文琪",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "好，我输了，你要怎样？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xing_ba_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_wen_qi",
      "text": "琪儿，回房去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    }
